     C* Nested DOW+IF: sum even 1..6 = 2+4+6 = 12
     C                     Z-ADD0         CNT
     C                     Z-ADD0         RPGRET
     C           CNT       DOWLE6
     C                     ADD  1         CNT
     C           CNT       DIV  2         Q
     C                     MVR            R
     C           R         IFEQ 0
     C                     ADD  CNT       RPGRET
     C                     END
     C                     END
